      "source": "### Interpretation\n\nThe first 10 rows, dataset shape, column information, and missing-value summary show that this is a genuine operational dataset with multiple QC sample types and partially populated control fields. That is useful evidence because real LIMS exports are often incomplete by design: standards and blanks may have explicit limits, while replicate-style records rely more on parent values and status fields.\n"
