    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": "### Interpretation\n\nThese engineered features convert raw QC records into more informative signals. Deviation measures how far a result is from its expected value, rolling statistics highlight local instability over time, RPD measures relative disagreement against a parent result, and recovery percentage is included for completeness even though this real dataset contains no matrix spike rows.\n"
    },
